&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This online session will be&amp;nbsp;facilitated via Zoom&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;by Caitlin DeClercq, Senior&amp;nbsp;Assistant Director of Graduate Student Programs and Services at the CTL.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Registrants will be emailed a Zoom link prior to the start of the session. Please note that registration closes at 11:55pm on September 1st. For same-day registration, please email&amp;nbsp;CTLgrads@columbia.edu.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
