&lt;p&gt;A conversation with&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://worldleaders.columbia.edu/directory/alok-sharma" target="_blank"&gt;Alok Sharma&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
